title_en: 1931 Willie Haney Letters, Pt. 06 [The Rabbit wants to marry his sister-in-law]
comment: "The Rabbit wanted his sister[in]law to be his wife and told tale to his wife and went out hunting act it has been told"

sentences.full_text: Chokfot etafenon lok estoklachekon epanak ayaktawa hokahlash.

original.original_gloss: I will get both together as wife
we just well as go home
